'''第56届奥斯卡颁奖典礼'''是[[电影艺术与科学学院|电影艺术与科学学院]]旨在奖励[[1983年电影|1983年电影]]的颁奖晚会，于[[太平洋时区|太平洋时区]]1984年4月9日晚六点（[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]晚九点）在洛杉矶[[多萝西·钱德勒大厅|多萝西·钱德勒大厅]]举行，共计颁发23类[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（又称学院奖）。晚会通过[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]直播，小杰克·海利制作，马蒂·帕赛塔执导<ref name="Pasetta">{{cite book | last = Osborne | first = Robert | title = 70 Years of the Oscar: The Complete History of the Academy Awards | year = 1999 | isbn = 978-0-7892-1142-2 | location = New York, New York, United States | publisher = Abbeville Publishing Group | page = 341}}</ref>，谈话节目主持、笑匠[[约翰尼·卡森|约翰尼·卡森]]第五次担任主持人。1979年的[[第51届奥斯卡金像奖|第51届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]是他首度主持，上一次是1982年的[[第54届奥斯卡金像奖|第54届]]。<ref>{{cite news | last = Steinberg | first = David | title = The Gold Standard | dead-url = no | url = https://www.latimes.com/la-mag-feb082009-theear-story.html | accessdate = 2021-09-08 | work = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | date = 2009-01-30 | archive-date = 2021-07-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210729095424/https://www.latimes.com/la-mag-feb082009-theear-story.html }}</ref>[[瓊·考琳絲|瓊·考琳絲]]与[[阿诺·施瓦辛格|阿诺·施瓦辛格]]九天前（3月31日）在加利福尼亚州[[比佛利山|比佛利山]][[比弗利希尔顿酒店|比弗利希尔顿酒店]]主持仪式颁发[[奧斯卡科技成果獎|奧斯卡科技成果獎]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Past Scientific & Technical Awards Ceremonies | url = http://www.oscars.org/awards/scitech/pastawards.html | publisher = [[电影艺术与科学学院|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] | access-date = 2014-10-07 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141007214118/http://www.oscars.org/awards/scitech/pastawards.html | archive-date = 2014-10-07 }}</ref>。

《[[親密關係_(電影)|母女情深]]》获[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]等五项大奖<ref>{{cite news | last = Harmetz | first = Aljean | title = 'Terms' Wins Best Picture; Duvall and Miss MacLaine Honored | dead-url = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/04/10/movies/terms-wins-best-picture-oscar-duvall-and-miss-maclaine-honored.html | accessdate = 2021-09-08 | work = The New York Times | date = 1984-04-10 | archive-date = 2021-07-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210729093806/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/04/10/movies/terms-wins-best-picture-oscar-duvall-and-miss-maclaine-honored.html }}</ref>，其他获奖电影包括胜出三项的《[[芬妮和亚历山大|芬妮和亚历山大]]》与《[[太空先鋒_(電影)|太空先锋]]》，拿下两项的《[[怜情蜜意|怜情蜜意]]》，获奖一项的《[[男孩女孩|男孩女孩]]》、《5:15的弗拉门哥》、《[[闪电舞|闪电舞]]》、《[[他让我感到像在跳舞|他让我感到像在跳舞]]》、《[[纽约冰淇淋|纽约冰淇淋]]》、《[[危險年代|危險年代]]》、《[[燕特尔|燕特尔]]》。晚会的电视直播吸引4210万美国观众收看，[[尼爾森收視率|尼爾森收視率]]达30.3%。

== 入围与胜出 ==
1984年2月16日，学院主席吉恩·艾伦与演员[[米基·鲁尼|米基·鲁尼]]公布第56届奥斯卡金像奖入围名单<ref>{{cite news | title = Oscar Nominations Are Due | work = Baytown Sun | dead-url = no | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/83350953/oscar-nominations-are-due/ | access-date = 2021-09-08 | date = 1984-02-16 | page = 2-A | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2021-08-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210813083928/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/83350953/oscar-nominations-are-due/ }}</ref>。《[[親密關係_(電影)|母女情深]]》以十一项提名领跑，《[[太空先鋒_(電影)|太空先锋]]》八项紧随其后<ref>{{cite news | last = Harmetz | first = Aljean | title = 'Endearment' Tops Oscar Nominations | page = C21 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/02/17/movies/endearment-tops-oscar-nominations.html | accessdate = 2021-09-08 | work = The New York Times | date = 1984-02-17 | archive-date = 2021-07-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210729095425/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/02/17/movies/endearment-tops-oscar-nominations.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。获奖名单在4月9日的颁奖典礼揭晓。[[詹姆斯·L·布鲁克斯|詹姆斯·L·布鲁克斯]]成为史上第三位凭同一部电影获三项奥斯卡奖的导演、编剧、制片人<ref>{{Cite book | last = Jones | first = Arnold Wayne | title = The Envelope, Please: The Ultimate Academy Awards Trivia Book | url = https://archive.org/details/envelopepleaseul00jone | year = 1999 | isbn = 978-0-3807-9944-2 | location = New York, New York, United States | publisher = [[哈珀柯林斯|HarperCollins]] | page = [https://archive.org/details/envelopepleaseul00jone/page/250 250]}}</ref>。《[[芬妮和亚历山大|芬妮和亚历山大]]》凭四项胜出创下[[获奥斯卡金像奖的非英语电影|非英语片获奖数]]新纪录<ref name="HonoraryOscars">{{cite book | last1 = Kinn | first1 = Gail | last2 = Piazza | first2 = Jim | title = The Academy Awards: The Complete Unofficial History | year = 2002 | isbn = 978-1-5791-2396-3 | location = New York, New York, United States | publisher = Workman Publishing Company | page = 237}}</ref>{{refn|group="注"|此后已有《[[臥虎藏龍_(電影)|卧虎藏龙]]》（2000年）、《[[寄生上流|寄生上流]]》（2019年）均以四项胜出追平纪录<ref>{{cite news | last = Nilles | first = Billy | title = All the History Made at the 2020 Oscars | url = https://www.eonline.com/news/1121093/all-the-history-made-at-the-2020-oscars | accessdate = 2021-09-08 | publisher = [[E!|E!]] | date = 2020-02-09 | archive-date = 2021-03-02 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210302121830/https://www.eonline.com/news/1121093/all-the-history-made-at-the-2020-oscars }}</ref>。}}[[琳达·亨特|琳达·亨特]]身为女子在《危险年代》饰演男子获[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|最佳女配角奖]]，至今仍是唯一出演异性角色获奖的演员<ref name="Wiley-Bona-1996">{{cite book | last1 = Wiley | first1 = Mason | last2 = Bona | first2 = Damien | title = Inside Oscar: The Unofficial History of the Academy Awards | url = https://archive.org/details/insideoscarunoff0000wile | year = 1996 | isbn = 978-0-3454-0053-6 | location = New York, New York, United States | edition = 5 | oclc = 779680732 | publisher = Ballantine Books}}</ref>{{rp|1145}}。最佳原创歌曲奖得主[[艾瑞尼·卡拉|艾瑞尼·卡拉]]是首位在非表演类奖项胜出的非裔女子<ref>{{cite news | last = Scott | first = Mike | title = It Was a Big Night for ‘Green Book’; It Was a Bigger One for the N.O. Film Industry | url = https://www.nola.com/entertainment_life/article_0453dd3e-719b-58aa-947d-2257fdd1cb23.html | access-date = 2021-07-15 | work = The Times-Picayune | date = 2019-02-25 | archive-date = 2021-07-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210715210809/https://www.nola.com/entertainment_life/article_0453dd3e-719b-58aa-947d-2257fdd1cb23.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

