== 典礼信息 ==
[[File:Johnny_Carson_1970.JPG|缩略图]]主持第56届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]

1983年9月，美国电影艺术与科学学院第三次聘请制片人小杰克·海利担任奥斯卡颁奖典礼电视直播制作人<ref>{{cite news | last = Anderson | first = George | title = Triangle Tattler: 'Cats', 'Dreamgirls,' '42nd Street' to Tour | work = [[匹兹堡邮报|Pittsburgh Post-Gazette]] | date = 1984-09-20 | page = 24}}</ref>。学院主席吉恩·艾伦在公布消息的新闻稿表示：“我们很高兴能请小杰克·海利回归奥斯卡奖节目……他的出众才华能确保颁奖典礼充满创新和娱乐”<ref>{{cite web | title = Jack Haley Jr. to Produce the 56th Academy Awards Show | url = https://digitalcollections.oscars.org/digital/collection/p15759coll9/id/7985/rec/13 | publisher = Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences | access-date = 2021-09-09 | page = 1 | archive-date = 2021-07-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210729082044/https://digitalcollections.oscars.org/digital/collection/p15759coll9/id/7985/rec/13 | date = 1983-09-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。学院还在同月公布消息，颁奖典礼将由笑匠兼《[[约翰尼卡森今夜秀|今夜秀]]》主持人[[约翰尼·卡森|约翰尼·卡森]]主持。艾伦对此表示：“约翰尼是以往奥斯卡颁奖典礼持续提升、人气日益高涨的重要原因。我们非常高兴能再度依赖他的才智和魅力为本次特别娱乐活动增添姿彩”。<ref>{{cite news | title = People: Here's Johnny Once Again on Oscar Show | work = Akron Beacon Journal | date = 1983-09-11 | page = 2}}</ref>

另外还有多人参与颁奖典礼制作。音乐家[[昆西·琼斯|昆西·琼斯]]担任晚会音乐总监，指挥管弦乐队演奏开场曲目<ref>{{cite news | last = Shull | first = Richard K. | title = Oscars Not So Endearing | page = 15 | work = The Indianapolis News | date = 1984-04-10}}</ref>。[[秀兰·邓波儿|秀兰·邓波儿]]在电视直播开场时露面，谈起1935年在[[第7届奥斯卡金像奖|第七届奥斯卡颁奖典礼]]获[[奥斯卡青少年奖|青少年奖]]的经历<ref name="Wiley-Bona-1996" />{{rp|639}}。歌手小萨米·戴维斯与[[麗莎·明內利|麗莎·明內利]]在电视直播收尾时表演歌曲《轻歌曼舞好营生》<ref name="Wiley-Bona-1996" />{{rp|641}}。马蒂·帕塞塔任直播导演<ref name="Pasetta" />。以往的奥斯卡颁奖典礼都是在节目开始时公布投票规则，但本届晚会首次挪到结尾时段<ref name="Wiley-Bona-1996" />{{rp|641}}。

=== 最佳影片提名电影票房表现 ===
2月16日入围名单公布时，五部最佳影片奖入围电影在美国的总票房为1.5亿美元，其中《母女情深》以7291万美元居首，其后分别是收入5250万美元的《大寒》，进账1570万美元的《太空先锋》，收入844万美元的《怜情蜜意》，进账56万美元的《换装师》<ref>{{cite web | title = 1983 Academy Award Nominations and Winner for Best Picture | url = https://boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=1983&p=.htm | access-date = 2017-10-06 | publisher = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171006064531/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?yr=1983&p=.htm | archive-date = 2017-10-06 }}</ref>。

=== 专业评价 ===
《[[沃斯堡电讯星报|沃斯堡电讯星报]]》专栏作家杰瑞·科菲发文批评奥斯卡颁奖典礼沉闷至极，是“电影界一年一度的粗俗自我放纵，没有任何内容值得上过当的观众再度默默忍受”<ref>{{cite news | last = Coffey | first = Jerry | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/83351171/gullible-viewers-hooked-again-by/ | title = Gullible Viewers Hooked Again By Tedious Academy Awards | work = Fort Worth Star-Telegram | date = 1984-04-11 | accessdate = 2021-09-09 | page = 7D | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2021-08-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210813083114/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/83351171/gullible-viewers-hooked-again-by/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《[[奥斯汀美国政治家报|奥斯汀美国政治家报]]》影评人帕特里克·塔加特指出，“过去一周后回首，（上）周一的奥斯卡颁奖典礼毫无疑问沉闷至极，只不过可能算不上史上之最。”在他看来，晚会方方面面都不出预料，各奖项毫无惊喜不说，甚至连电视直播赖以生存的噱头都没有.<ref>{{cite news | last = Taggart | first = Patrick | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/83351179/unrewarding-oscar-shows-bright-spots/ | title = Unrewarding: Oscar Show's Bright Spots Few and Far Between | work = Austin American-Statesman | accessdate = 2021-09-09 | date = 1984-04-15 | page = 221 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2021-08-13 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210813083119/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/83351179/unrewarding-oscar-shows-bright-spots/ }}</ref>《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》电视评论员[[霍华德·罗森伯格|霍华德·罗森伯格]]称本届颁奖典礼观感不佳，三小时四十分钟时长就像电影《[[亂世兒女_(1975年電影)|巴里·林登]]》般一晃而过。晚会依然遵照传统做法，把最几乎所有最受关注的重要奖项全挤在最后半小时，再度证明这种做法思虑不周，离谱到愚蠢。<ref>{{cite news | last = Rosenberg | first = Howard | title = It Was Not an Endearing Oscarcast | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 1984-04-11 | page = F9}}</ref>

《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》电视专栏作家约翰·奥康纳写道：“精力充沛、和蔼可亲的卡森先生奠定并维持晚会基调”，他称赞卡森以惯常喜剧手段呈现颇显孩子气但又充满永恒魅力的格调<ref>{{cite news | last1 = O'Connor | first1 = John J. | title = Oscar Program: Long, But Different | page = C26 | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1984/04/11/arts/tv-review-oscar-program-different-but-long.html | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-09-09 | work = The New York Times | date = 1984-04-11 | archive-date = 2021-07-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210719092740/https://www.nytimes.com/1984/04/11/arts/tv-review-oscar-program-different-but-long.html }}</ref>。《[[巴尔的摩太阳报|巴尔的摩太阳报]]》影评人史蒂芬·亨特认为本届颁奖典礼与以往几年相比很有新意、节奏明快，最大优势就是正值巅峰状态的约翰尼·卡森回归主持<ref>{{cite news | last = Hunter | first = Stephen | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/83350915/endearment-wins-oscars-as-best-picture/ | title = 'Endearment' Wins Oscars as Best Picture | work = [[巴尔的摩太阳报|The Baltimore Sun]] | accessdate = 2021-09-09 | date = 1984-04-10 | page = A8 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2021-08-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210813083122/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/83350915/endearment-wins-oscars-as-best-picture/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。迈克·达菲在《[[底特律自由新聞|底特律自由新聞]]》发文，赞扬卡森主持对节目的提升不可估量，如珠妙语总能恰到好处地令人精神一振，他特别喜欢杰克·尼科尔森模仿[[蓝调兄弟|蓝调兄弟]]的桥段<ref>{{cite news | last = Duffy | first = Mike | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/83351193/sure-they-drag-but-the-oscars-are/ | title = Sure They Drag, but The Oscars Are Always Fun | page = 9D | work = [[底特律自由新聞|Detroit Free Press]] | date = 1984-04-11 | via = Newspapers.com | accessdate = 2021-09-09 | archive-date = 2021-08-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210813083116/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/83351193/sure-they-drag-but-the-oscars-are/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 收视与荣誉 ===
本届颁奖典礼通过[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]在美国直播，播出时段平均有4210万观众收看，与[[第55届奥斯卡金像奖|上一年]]相比下跌两成一<ref>{{cite news | accessdate = 2021-09-09 | archivedate = 2021-07-29 | dead-url = no | url = https://variety.com/2012/tv/news/crystal-social-media-fuel-oscar-ratings-1118050758/ | title = Crystal, social media fuel Oscar ratings | last = Kissell | first = Rick | date = 2012-02-27 | work = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20210729095425/https://variety.com/2012/tv/news/crystal-social-media-fuel-oscar-ratings-1118050758/ }}</ref>。节目的[[尼爾森收視率|尼爾森收視率]]也不及前一年，吸引30.3%的家庭观众，收视率约为五成<ref>{{cite news | title = Nielsen Ratings | work = The Philadelphia Inquirer | date = 1984-04-18 | page = E12}}</ref>。

1984年8月，第56届奥斯卡颁奖典礼获[[第36届黄金时段艾美奖|第36届黄金时段艾美奖]]四项入围<ref>{{cite web | title = The 56th Annual Academy Awards–Emmy Awards, Nominations and Wins | url = https://www.emmys.com/shows/56th-annual-academy-awards | publisher = Academy of Television Arts and Sciences | accessdate = 2021-09-09 | archive-date = 2021-07-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210729105406/https://www.emmys.com/shows/56th-annual-academy-awards | dead-url = no }}</ref>，同年九月拿下最佳综艺节目艺术指导奖<ref>{{cite news | last = Margulies | first = Lee | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/83351226/first-round-emmys-presented-moyers/ | title = First-Round Emmys Presented: Moyers' 'Walk,' J.F.K. Special Honored | work = Los Angeles Times | date = 1984-09-19 | page = I10 | via = Newspapers.com | accessdate = 2021-09-09 | archive-date = 2021-08-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210813083124/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/83351226/first-round-emmys-presented-moyers/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

